{"title":"Perfect Day","plot":"A film about a day in the life of Rick, an Irish forty-something who lives in Phuket, Thailand. He sets out to have what is for him the perfect day, a combination of hedonism and spirituality, traveling the island 'Easy Rider' style on a large chopper motorbike. However all is not as it seems with Rick. He is visited regularly by the ghost of his humorous dead father and haunted by memories of a girl called Clodagh. Through the course of the day he muses on his life, and considers how we went from the optimism of Live Aid to the horror of 9/11. Rick's secret past is discovered, a past which has led him to where he is now. Perfect Day is about priorities in life and how one man copes with his fate, in a film beautifully shot on location in Thailand and Ireland.","genres":["Drama"],"stems":["A","film","about","a","day","in","the","life","of","Rick",",","an","Irish","forty-someth","who","live","in","Phuket",",","Thailand",".","He","set","out","to","have","what","is","for","him","the","perfect","day",",","a","combin","of","hedon","and","spiritu",",","travel","the","island","'","Easi","Rider","'","style","on","a","larg","chopper","motorbik",".","Howev","all","is","not","as","it","seem","with","Rick",".","He","is","visit","regular","by","the","ghost","of","his","humor","dead","father","and","haunt","by","memori","of","a","girl","call","Clodagh",".","Through","the","cours","of","the","day","he","muse","on","his","life",",","and","consid","how","we","went","from","the","optim","of","Live","Aid","to","the","horror","of","9/11",".","Rick","'s","secret","past","is","discov",",","a","past","which","has","led","him","to","where","he","is","now",".","Perfect","Day","is","about","prioriti","in","life","and","how","one","man","cope","with","his","fate",",","in","a","film","beauti","shot","on","locat","in","Thailand","and","Ireland","."],"lemmas":["a","film","about","a","day","in","the","life","of","Rick",",","a","irish","forty-something","who","live",